metadata.name: The warrior
metadata.description:
PHOTO
This photo has been captured in the Passo Rolle and the mountain lighten by the first rays of the sun is called Cimon della Pala.
Took it during the 2021/2022 winter.
I left home at 3 a.m to reach the spot in time for the sunrise and at the Pass, the temperature was -16°C (3.2°F).
The spot I intended to reach was not far and I easily get there, but like always, the worst is staying there still and waiting for the sunrise, the wind started blowing and the temperature was lowering.
I got to stay there for an hour and half, then I moved down to meet some rays of sun to warm up.

Passo Rolle - Italy
